                  </p>
                  <div style={{ fontSize: '12px', color: '#6b7280' }}>
                    ÌïÑÏöî Î†àÎ≤®: {dungeon.requiredLevel} | Ï∏µÏàò: {dungeon.floors}Ï∏µ | ÌòÑÏû¨ Ï∏µ: {dungeon.currentFloor}Ï∏µ
                  </div>
                </div>
                <button
                  onClick={() => enterDungeon(dungeon)}
                  disabled={!dungeon.isUnlocked || character.level < dungeon.requiredLevel}
                  style={{
                    background: dungeon.isUnlocked && character.level >= dungeon.requiredLevel
                      ? 'linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%)'
                      : '#4b5563',
                    color: 'white',
